OL,3,CKeir Starmer travels to Middle East to
OL,4,C'support and sustain' ceasefire
OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fwelcomed a ceasefire agreement between
OL,8,Fthe US and Iran as he travels to the
OL,9,FMiddle East to meet leaders of Gulf
OL,10,Fcountries.
OL,12,F"I welcome the ceasefire agreement
OL,13,Freached overnight, which will bring a
OL,14,Fmoment of relief to the region and the
OL,15,Fworld," he said.
OL,17,F"Together with our partners we must do
OL,18,Fall we can to support and sustain this
OL,19,Fceasefire, turn it into a lasting
OL,20,Fagreement and reopen the Strait of
OL,21,FHormuz."
