OL,3,CKeir Starmer travels to Middle East to
OL,4,C'support and sustain' ceasefire
OL,6,FDowning Street said the Prime Minister
OL,7,Fwould use his visit to the Gulf on
OL,8,FWednesday make clear the UK's
OL,9,Fcommitment to de-escalation and hold
OL,10,Ffurther talks on "practical efforts"
OL,11,Fto restore freedom of navigation in
OL,12,Fthe Strait of Hormuz.
OL,14,FHe will also visit British military
OL,15,Fpersonnel in the region to thank them
OL,16,Ffor their service.
OL,18,FMore to follow...
